<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invalid Link - WorldBook</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #39195e 0%, #9c4ee6 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .reasons {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

            .reasons ul {
                margin: 10px 0 0 20px;
            }

            .reasons li {
                margin: 5px 0;
                color: #856404;
            }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #39195e;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

            a:hover {
                background-color: #9c4ee6;
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(142, 106, 222, 0.5);
            }

        @@media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-icon">❌</div>
        <h1>Invalid Link</h1>
        <p>Sorry, the password reset link is invalid or has expired.</p>

        <div class="reasons">
            <strong>Maybe because:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Link expired (15 minutes)</li>
                <li>Link already used</li>
                <li>Incorrect link</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Please <strong>request a new link</strong> to reset password.</p>

        <a href="/Logins/ForgotPassword">Back - New Link Request</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>